Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.86,0:00:03.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里見
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.65,0:00:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請給我零用錢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:12.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要多少
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.49,0:00:13.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 要給他嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.87,0:00:16.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 要很多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.71,0:00:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.75,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真給他啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.38,0:00:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.17,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\3c&H0203C6&\pos(433.5,38)}大塚村的惡夢再襲！？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.17,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正隶变_GBK\frz271\pos(1210,342)}出現怪病？復活的屍體
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.42,0:00:21.17,注释,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn@方正隶变_GBK\frz270.8\pos(1125,345)}本應死亡的五人接連復活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.30,0:00:23.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你知道關於這個事件的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:24.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.01,0:00:31.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具體的情況我也不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.60,0:00:35.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闖入禁忌之山的五個村民
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.64,0:00:39.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在回來後的一周後 全部死於謎樣的怪病
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:43.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個地區也有些奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.65,0:00:45.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是少有甘霖的土地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他背靠著一座被稱為「外持」的山
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.24,0:00:53.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如其名只有外持之山 會下「外持之雨」
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.71,0:00:57.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,外持？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.17,0:01:01.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂「外持」就是指特別對待的意思哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.63,0:01:04.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那魚就像一個人突然得到意外的好處一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.96,0:01:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 將只潤澤特定地區的雨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.01,0:01:12.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫做「外持之雨」
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.52,0:01:17.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,降在那座山上的雨變成地下水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.77,0:01:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總能讓我們順利種植作物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.90,0:01:24.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近連那水源也乾涸了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.95,0:01:30.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各位是樂師大人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.32,0:01:33.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感謝您特意邀我們到此
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.24,0:01:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡 發生了那種事件我還以為你們不會來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為是難得的村祭 想要辦得華麗些
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.33,0:01:44.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 請隨我去村長家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:48.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旦開野
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.12,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.58,0:01:56.12,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:59.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.12,0:01:59.52,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's me. Is that so pretty
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:03.99,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.52,0:02:03.99,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}You cann't choose my fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:10.30,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}乾いた風に抱かれて
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.90,0:02:10.30,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}迎面吹著乾燥的風
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:16.77,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}生命への 真偽を覚え 刻む想い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:16.77,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}懂得了生命的真偽 銘刻於心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:20.18,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}ただ 傍に居たいと願い
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.77,0:02:20.18,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}只是 祈願待在你身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.75,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}人を愛し 人を憎み
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.18,0:02:22.75,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}愛過 恨過
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:26.25,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲しさは  優しさ生む
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.75,0:02:26.25,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}悲傷最後化作溫柔
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:31.22,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}例え光が 消えたとしても
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.25,0:02:31.22,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}就算陷入無盡黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.99,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}明日の希望を探すよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.22,0:02:35.99,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}仍會尋覓明日希望
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:40.30,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃えた血の呼吸 消え寄せれば
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.99,0:02:40.30,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}燃燒的血液 停止了呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:45.37,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果は奇跡に変わる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:45.37,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}因果之緣 最終轉化成奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.57,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.37,0:02:47.57,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}So so so wonderland
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:50.04,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.57,0:02:50.04,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Shadow wish go to
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:53.78,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}闇を搔き分け
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.04,0:02:53.78,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}撥開黑暗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:57.61,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}手を伸ばすよ どこまでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.78,0:02:57.61,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}伸手向前 追尋你到任何地方
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.88,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.61,0:02:59.88,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}It's the worst key
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:03.52,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}いつか 変えるまで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.88,0:03:03.52,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}總有一天 命運將會轉變
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:08.19,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}涙の意味 無駄にはしない
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.52,0:03:08.19,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}不要讓眼淚白流
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:12.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}螺旋のように 蠢く果てに
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:12.83,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}如螺旋一般交織騷動的盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.83,OP_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}吠えて 交わる FATE
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.83,0:03:15.83,OP_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2\fad(0,400)}狂吠吧 交織的命運
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.02,0:03:30.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五個男人為了尋找新的水源進入了山中
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.19,0:03:33.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼那裡禁止進入呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.45,0:03:37.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村中流傳著那座山中自古以來住著猿神的傳說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.62,0:03:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擅入者有去無回
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.83,0:03:42.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這五人卻回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.96,0:03:47.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,徘徊在山中 即將餓死之際
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.46,0:03:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說出現了一位美麗的女性
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:55.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人為五人指出了回到村裡的路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.72,0:03:58.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還贈與了他們水喝
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.77,0:04:03.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後 就像五年前的大塚村一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人…把水…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.94,0:04:11.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里見先生
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.15,0:04:13.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到信乃了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.24,0:04:17.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經到午飯的時間了 卻不見他出現
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.53,0:04:21.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他一定會去 沒想到一個人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.29,0:04:22.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.04,0:04:25.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介 馬上去追信乃比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:27.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.88,0:04:38.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的是只在這座山中下雨啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.01,0:04:40.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.52,0:04:46.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明珠在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.02,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的和莊介的都在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止發過光嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.86,0:04:55.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.16,0:05:08.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又夢到那個男人了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.54,0:05:10.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.76,0:05:24.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我的一切…奪走的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.85,0:05:29.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在五年前的大塚村也出現了一個女人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.52,0:05:33.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和信乃 濱路能倖免於難
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.61,0:05:35.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是因為陪伴健康狀況崩潰的信乃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:39.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在鄰村的療養所療養的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行 記憶一片模糊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.45,0:05:46.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小文吾先生
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.12,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您為什麼來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.46,0:05:52.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來送客人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.96,0:05:55.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你在找信乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.76,0:05:56.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到他了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.76,0:06:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到他坐上了去西邊的電車
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.93,0:06:02.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還是來晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.18,0:06:04.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他果然是擅自跑出來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.93,0:06:08.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道他要去哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.02,0:06:11.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我正要去追他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.52,0:06:13.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去追信乃嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.40,0:06:16.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大哥 不要突然出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.95,0:06:21.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下一班西行的列車還要等兩個小時
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.57,0:06:24.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一副幹勁十足的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:26.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去廚房準備些便當
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.66,0:06:28.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.75,0:06:33.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他丟下你一個人去的地方 說明不是什麼好地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帶兩隻鬼過去 可以充當保鏢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.18,0:06:41.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那還真是讓人安心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.18,0:06:46.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說我們所前往的山裡會出現猿神
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.10,0:06:48.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 又扯上怪物了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.94,0:06:57.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村雨…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.40,0:07:01.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.28,0:07:06.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莊介的玉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.00,0:07:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 找不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.64,0:07:32.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有沒有看到和這個一樣的珠子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.07,0:07:38.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是對我很重要的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.19,0:07:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我的青梅竹馬寄放在我這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:45.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是丟了的話 就麻煩了
